comments: Approximation to e, accurate to 7 decimal places.
links: Harry J. Smith, Table of n, a(n) for n=1,...,20000
prog: (PARI) { default(realprecision, 20080); x=(Pi^4 + Pi^5)^(1/6); for (n=1, 20000, d=floor(x); x=(x-d)*10; write("b060302.txt", n, " ", d)); } [From _Harry J. Smith_, Jul 03 2009]
author: Jason Earls (zevi_35711(AT)yahoo.com), Mar 26 2001
